Welcome to Lin OS!

You are on the live ISO. To install Lin OS to your disk, double-click the
"Install Lin OS" icon on the desktop, or open a terminal and run:

    sudo calamares

Documentation:  https://github.com/salom600/lin/tree/main/docs
Issues:         https://github.com/salom600/lin/issues

Default live user: lin / lin
Default root user: root / lin
